======================================

Oneiroi NT is a port of Befaco's Oneiroi patch to the Expert Sleepers
Disting NT module format.  It is distributed under GPL-3.0-or-later
(see LICENSE).

The following components are vendored or derived from upstream projects.
Their original copyright holders remain the authors of their respective
contributions; see each section for details.


